uientry.unicode:
This is the number of turns until Ariel completes her ritual. If the timer reaches 0 the final battle will be triggered.

The number of turns until the final battle can be increased by completing the missions to destroy the Waystones.

Once three Waystones have been destroyed the final battle can be manually triggered.

[[col:red]]Losing the final battle will cause you to lose the campaign![[/col]]
